SpamOn,is,a,free,service,that,provides,disposable,e,mail,addresses,when,users,fill,out,forms,register,on,websites,or,meet,new,people,The,API,allows,users,to,integrate,SpamOn,data,on,their,website,or,application,There,is,currently,no,restrictions,on,the,number,of,queries,allowed,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON